= To account the whole width of the content, the margin is excluded

        FINAL ELEMENT WIDTH = left_border + left_padding + width +
                              right padding + right border.

= The height do the same

        FINAL ELEMENT HEIGHT = top_border + top_padding + height +
                               bottom_padding + bottom_border

= If you confuse why left_border/right_border/bottom_border/top_border is 
  include when account the FINAL ELEMENT WIDTH
  = It's because the border has thickness of its line.